<lb n="2"/><handShift new="m2"/>ἔτους <num value="13">τρ<supplied reason="lost">ε</supplied>ισκαιδεκάτου</num> μηνὸς <app type="alternative"><lem><unclear>Π</unclear><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></lem><rdg><unclear>Π</unclear><supplied reason="lost">αχων</supplied></rdg><rdg><unclear>Π</unclear><supplied reason="lost">αυνι</supplied></rdg></app> <num value="29"><supplied reason="lost">ἐνάτῃ καὶ εἰκάδι</supplied></num>
<lb n="3"/>ἐν <supplied reason="lost">Ἡρακλ</supplied>έους πόλει τῆι ὑπὲρ Μέμ<unclear>φ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ιν. ὁμολογεῖ Ἀγαθόδωρος</supplied>
