<lb n="23"/>ἢ ὁ ἐπελθὼν ὑπὲρ αὐτοῦ Θεοδ<supplied reason="lost">ώ</supplied>ρῳ <supplied reason="lost">ἐπίτιμον ἀργυρίου ἐπισήμου</supplied>
<lb n="24"/>Πτολεμαικοῦ νομίσματος <unclear>δ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ρ</supplied><unclear>α</unclear><supplied reason="lost">χμὰς</supplied> <num><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></num> <supplied reason="lost">καὶ τὸ</supplied>
